name: X-Ray P250 Package
description: This package contains a single custom painted P250 showing its internals with an X-Ray. P250 is a low-recoil firearm with a high rate of fire, which is a relatively inexpensive choice against armored opponents.

name: CS20 Case
description: Celebrating the 20th Anniversary of Counter-Strike, this weapon case contains a variety of weapon finishes from Steam Community Workshop and features the Classic Knife as the rare special item, a classic of the Counter-Strike series.

loot_list.name: Classic Knife
loot_list.footer: or the Exceedingly Rare Classic Knife!

name: CS20 Sticker Capsule
description: Celebrating the 20th Anniversary of Counter-Strike, this capsule contains a variety of stickers from Steam Community Workshop.

name: Half-Life: Alyx Collectible Pins Capsule
description: This capsule contains a single collectible pin commemorating Half-Life: Alyx, Valve's VR return to the Half-Life series. Collectible pins can be displayed on your profile.

name: Half-Life: Alyx Sticker Capsule
description: This capsule contains a variety of stickers commemorating Half-Life: Alyx, Valve's VR return to the Half-Life series.
